Mo thi TOEIC Part 6: in vo on vn
Tm tt li mt s mo thi TOEIC p dng cho part 5 v c th p dng cho part 6:
Xc nh t loi cn in: Khi bit c y l cu hi v t loi th iu u tin cn
lm l phn on xem t loi cn thiu l t loi no: tnh t, trng t, danh t hay ng
t. Sau , tm loi t trong 4 phng n. Thng thng, nhng cu hi ny khng
cn phi dch cu.
Hc cc t thng i chung vi nhau (collocations). Chng ta s ni jealous of
somebody ch khng ni jealous with somebody nh khi chng ta dch t ting Vit sang
Anh.
Lu th ca cc cu. Nu trong cu c du hiu nh in 2020, th chc hn ng t
trong cu phi chia mt trong nhng th tng lai ch khng th no l qu kh c.
Vic phn on nhanh, loi tr cc p n sai da vo cc mo nh s gip chng ta
tit kim c rt nhiu thi gian lm part 6 chng ta tp trung lm part 7 cho tt.
Ngoi ra, di y l 1 s mo dnh ring cho Part 6:
c ngay vo ch bi hi v ni dung cc p n. Khi lm bi part 6, chng ta cn
c ngay vo ch bi hi, khng cn c c bi. Sau , xc nh loi cu hi bi a ra
(t loi, ng php, t vng).
Nu hi v t loi hoc ng php th ch cn xem ch cn in v t xung quanh n,
khng cn c c cu. Trong trng hp cu cha cung cp thng tin tr li,
hy c nhng cu xung quanh gip chn phng n ng (thng l nhng cu
pha trn).
Theo cu trc thi TOEIC mi 2021 nm 2019, s c 1 cu trong bi Part 6 yu cu
bn chn c mt cu vo ch trng, thay v ch mt t.
Khc vi vic in mt t, khi in mt cu vo on vn, bn cn xem cc cu xung
quanh ch trng ny (thng l cu lin trc v cu lin sau) hiu c ngha c
bn ca on vn ri in cu hp ngha nht vo gia. Loi cu hi ny s yu cu bn
phi hiu on vn nhiu hn v mt thi gian lm bi hn lc trc mt cht.
